name: Annoyed
alt: Naomi with her hands on her hips, looking away with an annoyed expression.
description: Something made her mad, was it you?

name: Block
alt: Naomi pointing to the block button from a Discord menu.
description: She's just teasing you. Probably.

name: Blush
alt: Naomi brushing her hair from her face, smiling and blushing softly.
description: She'll play it off, but she probably appreciates whatever you said.

name: Cheer
alt: Naomi raising her hands and grinning
description: She believes in you. You got this!

name: Cry
alt: Naomi rubbing tears from her eyes.
description: Awww, she's sad...

name: Cute
alt: Naomi pointing at herself with a smile.
description: She's feeling cute right now.

name: Dancy
alt: Naomi twisting her torso back and forth, swinging her arms.
description: She does love to dance.

name: Dead
alt: Naomi laying down, her arms and legs stretched, playing dead.
description: She's not really dead, though she might be dead inside.

name: Drink
alt: Naomi holding a bottle of scotch whiskey, making a peace sign with her other hand.
description: Oh how she loves to drink.

name: Evil
alt: Naomi pushing her fingers together, devil horns on her head.
description: Whatever she's planning... run!

name: Facepalm
alt: Naomi placing her hand on her face in disbelief.
description: Did that really just happen?

name: Fight
alt: Naomi winding up to throw a punch.
description: Someone is about to get hit.

name: Giggle
alt: Naomi giggling, her hand over her mouth.
description: She does enjoy a good joke!

name: Grin
alt: Naomi grinning, eyes closed.
description: Naomi is generally a happy person.

name: Gun
alt: Naomi stretching her arm out, making a gun with her fingers.
description: Pew pew~!

name: Hello
alt: Naomi waving and smiling.
description: Hello~! Want to be friends?

name: Here
alt: Naomi jumping and spinning on one foot.
description: I'm Naomi! Look at me!

name: Huh
alt: Naomi with a confused look.
description: Did you really just do that?

name: Innocent
alt: Naomi pushing her hair from her face, a halo over her head.
description: I'm innocent, I swear. No really.

name: Kiss
alt: Naomi blowing a kiss.
description: Mwah!

name: Naomato
alt: Naomi blushing bright red, her eyes wide.
description: Wow, something really has her flustered.

name: Nya
alt: Naomi making claws with her hands.
description: Nya nya~!

name: Pat
alt: Naomi receiving a headpat.
description: She really loves headpats.

name: Peek
alt: Naomi peeking over the bottom of the screen.
description: I see you. You don't see me.

name: Ping
alt: Naomi holding a red notification icon, looking mad.
description: Did that really warrant a ping?

name: Plead
alt: Naomi pressing her fingers together and giving a pleading look.
description: She's scared to ask, but really wants it.

name: Please
alt: Naomi holding her hands out in a begging gesture.
description: Please don't make me beg.

name: Pout
alt: Naomi giving an annoyed pout.
description: Oh really? Come on now.

name: Rave
alt: Naomi in a cybersuit, doing the zero two dance.
description: She does love a good party.

name: Sad Cat
alt: Naomi doing the sad cat dance.
description: Someone begged her to.

name: Salute
alt: Naomi with her hand on her forehead in a military salute.
description: Yes ma'am!

name: Shark
alt: Naomi grinning and pointing at her shark teeth.
description: I'm a chaos goblin, not a chaos shark!

name: Shrug
alt: Naomi raising her hands and shrugging her shoulders.
description: She either doesn't know, or doesn't care.

name: Shy
alt: Naomi with her hand behind her head and a shy expression.
description: It takes a lot to make her feel shy...

name: Sing
alt: Naomi holding a microphone, raising her hand and singing.
description: She's a terrible singer, but she gets into the music when no one's around.

name: SMH
alt: Naomi with her hands on her head, shaking it.
description: smh my head my head

name: Sneak
alt: Naomi crouching down, a finger to her lips to shush someone.
description: She thinks she's sneaky, at least.

name: Stare
alt: Naomi leaning forward, staring at the screen.
description: She has to look closely to believe it.

name: Sunglasses
alt: Naomi pointing upward, wearing the thug life sunglasses
description: She's not nearly as cool as she thinks she is.

name: Sweat
alt: Naomi with her hands behind her head, nervously smiling.
description: Well... that didn't go as planned.

name: Thankiess
alt: Naomi bowing forward in thanks.
description: She truly appreciates it.

name: Think
alt: Naomi with her hand on her chin, deep in thought.
description: She's either thinking about code or Miku.

name: This
alt: Naomi looking and pointing up.
description: Nice! She agrees with you!

name: Victory
alt: Naomi jumping in excitement before doing a victory salute.
description: We did it! We won!

name: Wavey
alt: Naomi jumping and waving with both hands.
description: She's very excited to see you!

name: Wiggle
alt: Naomi wiggling her hips.
description: Wiggle wiggle wiggle...

name: Wink
alt: Naomi winking and making peace signs with both hands.
description: She can't help but be flirty in everything she does.

name: Woah
alt: Naomi gasping in surprise, holding her hands to her mouth.
description: It's either a good surprise or a bad surprise.

name: Work
alt: Naomi holding a laptop with one hand, typing with the other.
description: She's always working, even when she's on the go.

name: Yawn
alt: Naomi yawning, hand over her mouth.
description: All the work means she doesn't get enough rest.
